199
00:14:55,707 --> 00:14:56,947
Ying's determination may be strong.

200
00:14:57,547 --> 00:14:59,587
But he has a special affection
for Zhu Yan.

201
00:15:00,508 --> 00:15:01,587
So I plan

202
00:15:01,908 --> 00:15:03,228
