Master.

557
00:31:45,240 --> 00:31:50,320
♪It's your sacred promise♪

558
00:31:51,280 --> 00:31:54,000
♪Cultivating amidst the fleeting time
of this mortal world♪

559
00:31:54,708 --> 00:31:55,508
Master,

560
00:32:03,228 --> 00:32:04,867
