and dining

657
00:36:34,867 --> 00:36:37,387
together all the time.

658
00:36:38,148 --> 00:36:40,467
You were no longer alone.

659
00:36:41,548 --> 00:36:43,387
In any case,

660
00:36:43,387 --> 00:36:44,228
I'll never leave you.

661
00:37:25,708 --> 00:37:27,188
