674
00:38:19,548 --> 00:38:20,307
Look at you.

675
00:38:21,068 --> 00:38:22,307
You have both magical powers

676
00:38:22,668 --> 00:38:23,867
and great cooking skills.

677
00:38:24,907 --> 00:38:26,548
